headline: TD Cowen Lowers PT on Paycom Software (PAYC) Stock
summary: Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE:PAYC) is one of the Oversold Fundamentally Strong Stocks to Buy Right Now. On January 8, TD Cowen analyst Jared Levine reduced the price objective on the company’s stock to $184 from $200 while keeping a “Buy” rating, as reported by The Fly.
